        <mxCell id="NRdIkYyu0jA6Rm0OKIPd-8" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;User should be able to Sign up/ Login / Logout&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;User should be able to browse different TV Shows/ Movies based on tiltle name.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;User should be able to search for movies / TV shows&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Should be able to watch in different resultions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;User should be able to choose different subscriber plans&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;User should have different payment methods&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
